channel.title: Make ticket on Discord
channel.description:
If you have account issues or purchase problems, please make a ticket in the Discord server https://discord.gg/keyauth
Making a ticket for reasons such as questions about an example, will result in the ticket being closed. You're supposed to make post on this community website for that.
